{"tid":987087,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚]洗面集中討論","createTime":"2019-01-19T04:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T06:03:56.000Z","uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ce4cac26f1e4d8113292df8ef5e87331f0b9e6","tid":987087,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"我相信洗面係護膚最重要一環<br />\n但原來冇洗面集中討論<br />\n手上有的： <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gih2qAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgih2qAe.jpg&h=23f9fe91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排名不分先後，只分開架與非開架<br />\n仲有完全冇人講的花開雪飄飄(點解冇影，一陣再講<br />\n產品要用一段時間先見到效果好唔好，希望各位巴絲打都share下自己覺得好/差的洗面<br />\n個人就覺得講差比講好更重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間公司想有人講好，比錢就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8368c0d430e7fe0cb531c84721b632879ce5643","tid":987087,"uid":220435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"Lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ed446b751eb21176f3fe1a76a6335259459b0","tid":987087,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"我家姐買左D NU SKIN產品幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9399f6d182d476f692c1f335acaa2a9c6331e9","tid":987087,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"我是油性敏感肌，有輕微玫瑰痤瘡<br />\nsample會留番有人想知再講，因為用一次根本咩都試唔出<br />\n用過的洗面 <br />\n1. ROSETTE 白泥淨白滑嫩洗面膏<br />\n零售價 約 hk $38<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/euePP4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuePP4X.jpg&h=7e5ea3d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用完乾到核爆，即扔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 資生堂 洗顏專科 超微米潔顏乳(升級版)120g<br />\n零售價 約 hk $40<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLr296J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLr296J.jpg&h=b3105ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開櫃平價貨黎講性價比最高<br />\n所以我會好推薦比油面窮學生用<br />\n膏狀，用約一cm加水起泡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WqHt5He.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWqHt5He.jpg&h=7b15d647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gS85ov5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgS85ov5.jpg&h=2d8ed591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清潔力強，用後皮膚輕微繃緊，所以我只推薦給油面窮學生/巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ef2a13b04123616b1c888afdb289e6128adf0f","tid":987087,"uid":130950,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"乾肌 男<br />\n用專科超乾<br />\nbiore 滋潤版 洗完唔乾但有一層莫係皮膚面 有時會敏感<br />\n舒特膚 溫和 但洗完都有啲乾<br />\n豆乳 洗完都會乾 剛剛洗完仲超&rsquo;傑&lsquo;<br />\n極潤 一樣<br />\n依家用緊mary kay1號 唔起泡 但至少洗完唔會乾 依家個天氣都係耐唔耐用埋爽膚水已經夠 但幾舊水1支"},{"pid":"4664ce290b6de9ff11c053c4583a9f0354a64e13","tid":987087,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"花開雪飄飄 薏苓洗臉泡<br />\n零售價 220hkd/100ml<br />\n聲稱功效: 保濕，美白，祛黑頭粉刺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHyUgTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHyUgTE.jpg&h=eab3ffd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天然手作野，含茯苓薏仁。味道:健康工房味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟起泡樽，我每次用三泵，圖為一泵份量<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E4KsBV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE4KsBV4.jpg&h=ebd53f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好薄的泡，估計原因是極少/無起泡劑<br />\n用後好保濕，感覺有層滑潤既野係皮膚表面，好似用完護髮素的頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮膚零繃緊，十分溫和，清潔力中等<br />\n雖然我覺得幾好，不過我唔會再買<br />\n原因1. 需要可以放室溫，但我都係覺得放雪櫃較安心，所以每次使用好麻煩<br />\n2. 拎貨麻煩，係唐樓，好似可以順豐，但要支野要雪唔想順豐<br />\n3. 我喜歡清爽不喜歡滑<br />\n4. 佢聲稱的功效我只同意保濕。美白來講我本身白，所以感受不到，但暗瘡印變淡與黑頭生既時間與我用其他洗面一樣。即是與佢無關。<br />\n適合比喜歡潤的絲打<br />\n呢個會寫的比較長係因為網上真係完全冇人講<br />\n因為健吾介紹先識呢間野(我好撚憎個小氣基佬，唔好以為我係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係唔錯，但基於上面講既原因，唔會再買"},{"pid":"2d641e9d3a05e626bd5412c9f67ed0068391acb3","tid":987087,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9ed446b751eb21176f3fe1a76a6335259459b0","tid":987087,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"我家姐買左D NU SKIN產品幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"唔係傳銷嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ef22dfb46dfc592673a162195a8d6ec313d808","tid":987087,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"額頭油但係臉乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c24f1d79b62e5709eeec17dca22eab5eda636b9","tid":987087,"uid":4174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"free plus 好唔好用？"},{"pid":"4065cff32a4d004d6cad3fb9c995232ca1873c42","tid":987087,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e90f68b49a34209a3598d6c90257098cbaa118b","tid":987087,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"有用連結<br />\n1. 成份查詢<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cosdna.com/cht/product.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosdna.com%2Fcht%2Fproduct.php&d=f2bff6myf7k9XGAe9m7VUhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=91feea24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cosdna.com/cht/product.php</a><br />\n2. 消委會報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2208832/潔面愈洗愈痕%E3%80%80消委會驗出9款含可致敏防腐劑的潔面產品【附名單】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2208832%2F%E6%BD%94%E9%9D%A2%E6%84%88%E6%B4%97%E6%84%88%E7%97%95%25E3%2580%2580%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA9%E6%AC%BE%E5%90%AB%E5%8F%AF%E8%8